OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FGerry Adams has arrived at the High
OL,7,FCourt in London for the start of a
OL,8,Fcivil trial in claims brought by three
OL,9,Fmen injured in Provisional IRA
OL,10,Fbombings.
OL,12,FThe men bringing legal action against
OL,13,Fthe former Sinn Fein president are
OL,14,FJohn Clark, a victim of the 1973 Old
OL,15,FBailey bombing in London, Jonathan
OL,16,FGanesh, a 1996 London Docklands
OL,17,Fbombing victim, and Barry Laycock, a
OL,18,Fvictim of the 1996 Arndale shopping
OL,19,Fcentre bombing in Manchester
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FThey all allege that Mr Adams was a
OL,7,Fleading member of the Provisional IRA
OL,8,Fon those dates, including of its Army
OL,9,FCouncil.
OL,11,FMr Adams denies that he had any role
OL,12,Fin the Provisional IRA and is opposing
OL,13,Fthe claim.
OL,15,FThe trio are seeking just #1 in
OL,16,Fdamages.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FThey claim Mr Adams "acted together
OL,7,Fwith others in furtherance of a common
OL,8,Fdesign to bomb the British mainland"
OL,9,Fand was "directly responsible" in
OL,10,Fvarious roles within the Provisional
OL,11,FIRA for decisions made to place
OL,12,Fdevices in 1973 and 1996.
OL,14,FAnne Studd KC, for the three men, said
OL,15,Fthey are seeking #1 for "vindicatory"
OL,16,Fpurposes and that their case is "not a
OL,17,Ffocus on their injuries".
OL,26,@nD@UOUpD@dO]qD@IOUqD@^O]wD@YOUwD@eO]xD@
OL,26,AaOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FShe said they want to show how 77-year-
OL,7,Fold Mr Adams was involved in the
OL,8,FProvisional IRA "in the course of that
OL,9,Fconflict and to show on the balance of
OL,10,Fprobabilities that he was as involved
OL,11,Fas the people who planted and
OL,12,Fdetonated those bombs".
OL,14,FShe also said Mr Adams was "directly
OL,15,Fresponsible for and complicit in those
OL,16,Fdecisions made by that organisation to
OL,17,Fdetonate bombs on the British mainland
OL,18,Fin 1973 and 1996".
OL,26,@pD@QOUtD@VO]vD@\OUzD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FMs Studd told the court that a
OL,7,F"jigsaw" of evidence from those who
OL,8,Fknew Mr Adams and those who knew of
OL,9,Fhim will prove the case against him.
OL,11,FShe added: "The claimants' case is
OL,12,Fthat none of these bombings in the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom mainland took place
OL,14,Fwithout the knowledge and agreement of
OL,15,Fthe defendant in his role in the
OL,16,FProvisional IRA and latterly as a
OL,17,Fmember of the seven-man Army Council."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@HO]sD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FShe concluded: "There is no doubt that
OL,7,Fthe defendant contributed to the peace
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland, but the claimants
OL,9,Fsay that on the evidence he also
OL,10,Fcontributed to the war."
OL,12,FLawyers for Mr Adams, who denies the
OL,13,Fclaims, said he "played an
OL,14,Finstrumental role in the peace process
OL,15,Fwhich culminated in the signing of the
OL,16,FGood Friday Agreement in April 1998,
OL,17,Fwhich brought an end to the decades-
OL,18,Flong conflict".
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@XO]uD@QOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FEdward Craven KC, representing Mr
OL,7,FAdams, said: "The defendant's alleged
OL,8,Ffactual and legal responsibility for
OL,9,Fthe claimants' injuries is strongly
OL,10,Fcontested, as is the claimants'
OL,11,Fability to bring these claims against
OL,12,Fthe defendant several decades after
OL,13,Fthe expiry of the applicable
OL,14,Flimitation period."
OL,16,FHe added that there is "no legal or
OL,17,Fpractical reason why these claims
OL,18,Fcould not have been issued long before
OL,19,F2022".
OL,26,@oD@NOUvD@SO]xD@XOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,FMr Craven continued: "Even if the
OL,7,Fclaim were not bound to fail on
OL,8,Flimitation grounds, the claim must
OL,9,Finevitably fail on the merits.
OL,11,F"The defendant strenuously denies any
OL,12,Finvolvement in the bombings."
OL,14,FHe also said: "The defendant has never
OL,15,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of, still
OL,16,Fless charged or convicted of, any
OL,17,Foffence in connection with any of the
OL,18,Fbombings.
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@AOUtD@]O]vD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773162679
OL,3,CIRA bomb victims are suing Gerry Adams
OL,4,Cfor #1 as High Court case begins
OL,6,F"Had law enforcement authorities been
OL,7,Fin possession of information which
OL,8,Fcreated a reasonable suspicion that
OL,9,Fthe defendant may have been involved
OL,10,Fin those bombings, he would have been
OL,11,Farrested and questioned."
OL,13,FMr Adams arrived at the High Court in
OL,14,FWestminster this morning for the first
OL,15,Fday of the trial which is expected to
OL,16,Fend next week.
OL,18,FThe trial is expected to conclude next
OL,19,Fweek.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]
